{"tid":1505292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請接受現實 有人成功喺連登帶風向","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T14:15:06.000Z","uid":6845,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"066267f8c23b5eafecb5ad14c1eb761501efdc73","tid":1505292,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"請接受現實連登有人成功帶風向<br />\n<br />\n琴日一役之後 應該大家都預料到今日情況只會比琴日惡劣 今日咁多手足比人拉真係突發咩?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GebBH9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGebBH9Z.jpg&h=e3420cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你唔一早講?<br />\n一直都好多人講!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機場唔係冇人推 而係一直比人壓低<br />\n人鏈之後果日要早上5點起身入機場, 之後1點要到觀塘<br />\n係咪無人去先係合理呀?  你得我得係咪所有人都得?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聽日想入機場而放棄荃葵青既人同我入撚黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1501342\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1501342</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">荃灣義士比人斬 唔去當義士condom</span><br />\n依加地區戰又唔係燒黑社會燒警署燒popo  機場經濟癱瘓黎報仇係咪仲有效?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">排左期一讓再讓 又要改期當荃葵青condom?</span><br />\n局勢變化大 點解要堅持一成不變? 如果認同機場係有成效 一日機場一日地區唔係仲好?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點做得切機場文宣?</span><br />\n大家係咪唔記得812機場點開始?  就係811爆眼呀 一晚都文宣得切<br />\n2019啦 你估廿年前既資訊流通速度? 大把人無telegram 但係佢地會有ig fb 蘋果 立場 以上都無既人有幾多個? 佢平時靠飛鴿傳書先知遊行資訊架?<br />\n<br />\n咁以後唔洗勇武 <br />\n觀塘係咪傷唔夠?  狗鐵以後事前停地鐵就全世界入機場 迫到佢以後唔敢停地鐵先得唔得呀<br />\n一日地區一日機場比人休息得唔得呀 <br />\n你以為和理非活動前線手足唔洗出黎? 事實就係愈黎愈少人 佢地要頂硬上 之前機場大把人連踩5日 唔出嘅都係唔出 第一線俾人拉左 就第二線補上 所以愈黎愈弱 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最後想講嘅係今日之後再冇藉口唔入機場 <br />\n一個星期最少一日總動員機場好嗎</span>"},{"pid":"c9d8f5ffd8b6a40073a7322ee0eb73354b213769","tid":1505292,"uid":114956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:14.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"f76b1e912e76dfe540c248b16420ba329d3a59b0","tid":1505292,"uid":114956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"bb2bd63872f128ad1dcc3b6b853df2e677d5ee8a","tid":1505292,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeaZGrM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeaZGrM.gif&h=2ea5b072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n831 中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n901 塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n9月三罷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不分和勇！永不割席！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 請為自由而戰<br />\nFight for freedom, Stand with Hong Kong</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span><br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our times</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"55edbac639e4b6b0b5e0f1a1ecfa4dfe93609f4b","tid":1505292,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"要食雞 和 和尚"},{"pid":"a1cd1ff26b9837c26110c88244bc1137e92b8d3f","tid":1505292,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"唔係壓底機場 而係成日都早一日叫人入 仲要撞左其他活動<br />\n可否book番一日無其他野大家一齊入咪得"},{"pid":"0e12d12189d590f031649f2be76f528c64693e12","tid":1505292,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"我淨係知機場帶風